- No longer use defer-chain but call exec instead for onboot and onexception;
- The >link can be negative only and 9-bits when using a single byte;
- Allocate big buffer for the implementation of module;
- Allow change of offset for dump word (relative address);
- Improve the dict module (allow removal of first dictionary in context and
  arbitrary dictionary from context);
- Maybe dict>next should become universal >next;
- Add floating point support to the VM;
